reviewText: I LOVE all animal shows so this is a hit for me
Great show for kids that like animals with the legendary Jack Hanna. The show is a dated but still good.
Wonderful way to learn about wildlife
GOOD SHOW. GOOD HOME SCHOOL TOOL. FROM RGB IN TN.
Gave it to my grandson for Christmas.  A big hit.  We watch Jack Hanna's program on TV every Saturday.  Wonderful.
